
1. Install CellProfiler from their website http://www.cellprofiler.org/

2. Create a local Script that is in the Bisque Path i.e. /usr/local/bin/CellProfiler

-----------------------
cat > /usr/local/bin/CellProfiler <<EOF
#!/usr/bin/env sh
unset VIRTUAL_ENV
JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun/jre/lib/amd64/server
export JAVA_HOME LD_LIBRARY_PATH
exec /usr/bin/python /usr/local/CellProfiler/CellProfiler.py $*
EOF
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/CellProfiler 
-------------------------

3.  Enjoy.
